Description_lang: Consuming Killing Machine fires a Glacial Advance through your target at $s1% effectiveness.

description_blz.en_US: Consuming Killing Machine fires a Glacial Advance through your target at 80% effectiveness.
description_blz.es_MX: Consumir Máquina de matar desata un Avance glacial que atraviesa a tu objetivo con una eficacia del 80%.

description_blz.zh_TW: 消耗殺戮酷刑，朝目標發射冰川突進，但效果強度變為80%。
